        <div xml:id="dedicatees">
            <head>Dedicatee:</head>
            <p> Caroline Miolan-Carvalho (<date>1827–95</date>), leading soprano during the Second Empire and
                wife of Léon Carvalho, director of the Théâtre-Lyrique. In <date>1867</date> she created the role
                of Juliette in Gounod’s <title rend="italics">Roméo et Juliette</title>.</p>
        </div>


